      "writtenOn": "2018-04-05T00:53:58Z",
      "side": 0,
      "message": "The client now makes an attempt to open the memory file itself. If that fails, it sends a kOpenMemoryFile request to the broker and creates a BrokeredMemory. The result of the open isn\u0027t currently used, but maybe it would be interesting to record to know how often we\u0027re falling back to ptrace peek.",
